{"tid":1819522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好大粒花生 竟然冇人知？小粉紅怒屌葛珮帆！","createTime":"2020-01-11T01:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T04:48:08.000Z","uid":291309,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c987c5768c42b3c079da125fcc1af170a696f5f0","tid":1819522,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T01:09:03.000Z","msg":"前幾日民建聯拉大隊去中聯辦要求交代武漢肺炎程況<br />\n微博小粉紅大怒，對&ldquo;交代&rdquo;二字非常有意見<br />\n認為民建聯不知道自己幾斤幾兩，竟然要求上級交代<br />\n話建制和港府在搞小朝廷<br />\n仲被睇穿左新官上任來摸底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「民建聯借此來探口風是真，畢竟心虛了。」<br />\n<br />\n      「香港的建制派沒別的事做了嗎？武漢不明肺炎還要怎麼通報？」<br />\n<br />\n「難怪建制派會輸，難怪見不到新主任。」<br />\n<br />\n      「止暴制亂半年多沒見做什麼，難怪建制派會輸得一塌糊塗，估計還會繼續輸。」<br />\n<br />\n「泛民是無恥，建制則是陰險。」<br />\n<br />\n更多詳情自己上葛博士微博睇，好精彩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oekfbv0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOekfbv0.png&h=1e153f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QJgFpm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QJgFpm.png&h=24798042&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwWJ4Q2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwWJ4Q2.png&h=b969326c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jfkria3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfkria3.png&h=879d59d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jYcYa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jYcYa5.png&h=2fd0afe4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGJ4PhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGJ4PhM.png&h=4e73dfb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rf21Rv7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRf21Rv7.png&h=e0f63c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWhdHCN.png\